article.description: — Tavin Lovan had 18 points as UAB easily defeated Troy 77-55 on Sunday.
article.headline: Lovan carries UAB over Troy 77-55
article.story: BIRMINGHAM, Ala. -- — Tavin Lovan had 18 points as UAB easily defeated Troy 77-55 on Sunday. Quan Jackson and Michael Ertel added 15 points each, and Trey Jemison had 13 points for UAB (4-0). Zay Williams had 17 points for the Trojans (1-3). Khalyl Waters added 16 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
